title: Slow cooker beef and vegetable soup
ingredients: ['1L beef stock, or more if needed', '3 carrots, roughly chopped', '1 large stick celery, roughly chopped', '1 1/2 tablespoons chopped fresh parsley', '1/2 teaspoon celery seed', '2 bay leaves', '450g lean minced beef', '1 onion, chopped', '1 clove garlic, minced, or to taste', '1 (400g) tin whole plum tomatoes', '2 potatoes, peeled and cut into bite-size pieces', '2 (198g) tins sweetcorn, drained', '1 (400g) tin haricots verts, drained', '1 (400g) tin petits pois, drained']
